# 🔥 2. CRUD Operations (Fetch)

## ✅ GET API

```js
const [data, setData] = useState([]);
const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);

useEffect(() => {
  fetchData();
}, []);

const fetchData = async () => {
  try {
    setLoading(true);
    const res = await fetch("https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/users");
    const result = await res.json();
    setData(result);
  } catch (err) {
    console.log(err);
  } finally {
    setLoading(false);
  }
};
```

